                            <p class="cards__description"> The project was focused on improving the user experience through the lens of responsive coding. The design brief was delivered in Figma thus allowing us to work collabortatively in our Pair-Programming sessions. Using media queries, css grid, image compression, and flexbox to create a beautiful, pixel-perfect, site wheter the user is viewing on the standard computer monitor or the smallest of phone screens.
