                            <p class="cards__description">JavaScript. Incorporates the use of my own chosen images, which vary in size but must fit in grid. User is able to change the profile name, information, and profile image. Using REST API and backend server support, the user is also able to upload their own photo the site and like photos left by others! Media query again for responsive design. Also used the :hover and :active features on classes.
